Louis De B. Moore, as Owner of THE Gas Yacht COQUETTE, Appellee, v. THE Yacht NATALON, Her Engines, etc., Appellant. No. 84. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Dec. 1, 1930. Neil P. Cullom and Henry W. Steingarten, both of New York City, for appellant. Park, Mattison & Lynch, of New York City (Anthony Y. Lynch, Jr., and John K. Hartley, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed.
